abstract: Democrat Jackie Biskupski defeats incumbent Ralph Becker in Salt Lake City mayoral race, becoming first openly gay person to hold position.
lead_paragraph: Jackie Biskupski has won Salt Lake City’s mayoral race, becoming the first openly gay person to hold the post.

headline.main: Utah: Salt Lake Mayor’s Race Settled
